{
  "texts": [
    "RQ1 addresses the reliability and quality of the evaluations.",
    "To answer this, we compared the different runs of each model on the exact text by calculating inter-class correlation, treating each run as an individual rater (see Section 4.1).",
    "For the following sections, the paper always considers the average of the ten runs as the final rating.",
    "In Section 4.2, we compared the assessments of the LLMs to those of real-world teachers using the Spearman correlation coefficient to identify similarities between the ratings.",
    "For RQ2, we examined the overall holistic scores alongside all multidimensional aspects, including both language-and content-related criteria (see Section 4.3)."
  ]
}